{"tid":1563232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"跳閘手足注意","createTime":"2019-09-12T10:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T02:03:24.000Z","uid":313417,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"db86767623aff1a37f3655115a96e060417c49f3","tid":1563232,"uid":313417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:30:02.000Z","msg":"老友車長又報料，風險變大，注意唔俾人捉到。<br />\n<br />\n有TIU同事話 可以嘅話通知兄弟們唔好再跳閘<br />\n班popo要我地d職員做完surcharge 另外再檢控附例4.1b<br />\n(即以正當使用供進出用的票閘、欄障或旋轉柵閘(如有的話)以外的方式進入或離開該等部分)<br />\n要上法庭審理 最高罰款$5000+有案底"},{"pid":"0e302e2bd512149abe65d32319a310ea6f4cc9ae","tid":1563232,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:30:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"daf88a6afc1583dc449a4194bcc2933eb70a70c6","tid":1563232,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:30:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"41712f2bf73b4d9df5aa1880141c38855042e1f8","tid":1563232,"uid":26937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:31:40.000Z","msg":"哇 跳個閘都有案底<br />\n好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07728f290d84409192b9631653f0721677b93b90","tid":1563232,"uid":235458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:31:41.000Z","msg":"咁如果用綠卡呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4dc3b91ffa5b29882b01b406f99cf822b9eab1","tid":1563232,"uid":22095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:32:16.000Z","msg":"我有飛架<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334f7d2d9c671bd78d58cfd8419469725d534e3a","tid":1563232,"uid":313417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:36:12.000Z","msg":"總之痴晒線，依條法例要黨鐵俾錢告，告上法庭麻煩到前線員工之外仲要罰款係政府袋。"},{"pid":"4eba3c02611ef414f14931e0eada646ee9336fdc","tid":1563232,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:03:24.000Z","msg":"和理非式搭鐵三寶：<br />\n1.正常八達通<br />\n2.綠卡<br />\n3.隨身已入閘單程飛一張（最平一個站既飛就得）<br />\n<br />\n出入當然用綠卡，如果遇到food panda查飛，因為佢地手上多數得八達通查飛機<br />\n<br />\n情境一：<br />\n已入閘時查飛，show 單程飛<br />\n<br />\n情境二：<br />\n出閘後查飛，show正常八達通<br />\n<br />\n情境三：<br />\n查到無效飛，無賴扮唔知/補飛/罰錢/9秒9"}]}